The paper deals with a data structure (suffix tree) and its parallel query, which falls under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The use of parallelism suggests that it may also belong to the categories of parallel computing (cs.DC) and computational complexity (cs.CC). The paper may also involve programming language concepts (cs.PL) and performance analysis (cs.PF) due to the discussion of work, time, and space complexity.
